==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: The gods are only a few feet above your head.
===Proverb===
{{cmn-proverb|t|pin=jŭtóu sān chĭ yŏu shénmíng|pint=ju3tou2san1chi3you3shen2ming2|tra=舉頭三尺有神明|sim=举头三尺有神明|rs=臼10}}
#  The gods are watching, so don't think you can get away with anything.
